headline: Tractor Supply (TSCO): Reassessing Valuation After Recent Pullback vs Long‑Term Return Strength
summary: Tractor Supply (TSCO) has been on a quieter stretch lately, but the stock’s recent pullback and mixed short term returns are starting to catch income focused and long term investors’ attention again.
